divs: Sighting DetailsI was letting my dog outside and looked at the sky(as I normally do), and noticed this object in the sky. I really didn't know what this object was. I ran through my mind what it could be...couldn't have been a satellite. The shape was off. It also wasn't moving in any way. I eventually had to go inside, so naturally I lost sight of the object. Whatever it was, it put me in a sense of wonderment.
Summary: I just saw this sock shaped object in the sky. It could be a V shaped object. The angle could've deformed it a bit.
